  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study seeks to determine whether social networking technologies can be used to increase
      HIV prevention and testing.The HOPE (Harnessing Online Peer Education) model seeks to apply a
      diffusion of innovations style intervention to social media to increase HIV testing.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
